{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777057802825,"sessionID":"ses_23f1ad229ffeRkk07R6QDybS6x","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_SmTEe5JitAroWDhfI0632AkQ","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\README.md","limit":220,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # mycli\n2: \n3: `mycli` 是 `D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library` 的统一命令入口。\n4: \n5: 它把能力包、脚本、现有 CLI 工具组织成一套可发现、可说明、可执行的命令体系。\n6: \n7: ## Usage\n8: \n9: ```powershell\n10: mycli --help\n11: mycli list\n12: mycli package list\n13: mycli package register <package/path> --summary <text> --source <text>\n14: mycli package register-full <package/path> --summary <text> --source <text> --commands <json> --help <markdown>\n15: mycli <package...> --help\n16: mycli <package...> list\n17: mycli <package...> command list\n18: mycli <package...> command register <name> --summary <text> --entry <absolute-path> --args <json> [--prefix-args <json>]\n19: mycli <package...> command register-many --commands <json>\n20: mycli <package...> command update <name> [--summary <text>] [--entry <absolute-path>] [--args <json>] [--prefix-args <json>]\n21: mycli <package...> help update --content <markdown>\n22: mycli <package...> <command> [args...]\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ## Core Ideas\n26: \n27: - `package`\n28:   一个能力包\n29: - `subpackage`\n30:   包下面的子包，目录即层级\n31: - `command`\n32:   包里的具体执行动作\n33: - `cli.package.json`\n34:   包注册中心\n35: - `README.md`\n36:   包级帮助内容来源\n37: \n38: ## Common Flows\n39: \n40: 查看所有顶层包：\n41: \n42: ```powershell\n43: mycli list\n44: ```\n45: \n46: 查看某个包的完整说明：\n47: \n48: ```powershell\n49: mycli opencode --help\n50: ```\n51: \n52: 查看某个包里有哪些子包和命令：\n53: \n54: ```powershell\n55: mycli opencode list\n56: ```\n57: \n58: 执行某个命令：\n59: \n60: ```powershell\n61: mycli opencode run \"hello\"\n62: ```\n63: \n64: 查看并使用 workflow 能力：\n65: \n66: ```powershell\n67: mycli agent-workflow --help\n68: mycli agent-workflow list\n69: mycli agent-workflow validate D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\agent-workflow\\examples\\script_echo_flow\n70: ```\n71: \n72: ## opencode Example\n73: \n74: `opencode` 目前同时支持两种方式：\n75: \n76: 直接映射命令：\n77: \n78: ```powershell\n79: mycli opencode run \"hello\"\n80: mycli opencode models --help\n81: mycli opencode agent --help\n82: ```\n83: \n84: 原生透传：\n85: \n86: ```powershell\n87: mycli opencode native --help\n88: mycli opencode native run hello\n89: mycli opencode native models --help\n90: ```\n91: \n92: ## agent-workflow Example\n93: \n94: `agent-workflow` 适合把多步骤任务建模成可运行、可等待、可审核的 workflow。\n95: \n96: ```powershell\n97: mycli agent-workflow init D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\my-flow --workflow-id my_flow --name \"My Flow\"\n98: mycli agent-workflow scaffold D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\my-flow\n99: mycli agent-workflow validate D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\my-flow\n100: mycli agent-workflow graph D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\my-flow\n101: mycli agent-workflow start-run D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\agent-workflow\\examples\\script_echo_flow\n102: ```\n103: \n104: 单次 agent 调用优先用 `mycli agent-cli run`。\n105: 多步骤、可等待、可审核、带运行状态的流程优先用 `mycli agent-workflow ...`。\n106: \n107: ## Docs\n108: \n109: 用户手册：\n110: \n111: - `D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\common\\user-manual.md`\n112: \n113: 维护与技术手册：\n114: \n115: - `D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\common\\technical-manual.md`\n\n(End of file - total 115 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# mycli\n\n`mycli` 是 `D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library` 的统一命令入口。\n\n它把能力包、脚本、现有 CLI 工具组织成一套可发现、可说明、可执行的命令体系。\n\n## Usage\n\n```powershell\nmycli --help\nmycli list\nmycli package list\nmycli package register <package/path> --summary <text> --source <text>\nmycli package register-full <package/path> --summary <text> --source <text> --commands <json> --help <markdown>\nmycli <package...> 